FROM python:slim-buster

# Install dependencies
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir six

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir pdfkit

VOLUME ["/var/imapbox/"]

# Copy source files and set entry point
COPY *.py /opt/bin/
ENTRYPOINT ["python", "/opt/bin/imapbox.py"]
